trans-unit.source: Invokes a standard [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win#initcap](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-winsharpinitcap-md.md)] print dialog box that configures a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> and <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> according to user input and then prints a document.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer en standard [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win#initcap](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-winsharpinitcap-md.md)] utskriftsdialogboksen som konfigurerer en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> i henhold til brukerinndata og skriver ut et dokument.

trans-unit.source: A user can use the **Print** dialog box to select a printer, configure it, and perform a print job.
trans-unit.target: En bruker kan bruke den **skrive ut** for å velge en skriver, konfigurere den og utføre en utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: Strictly speaking, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialog.PrintDocument%2A> method without ever opening the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Praksis kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialog.PrintDocument%2A>metoden uten å måtte åpne dialogboksen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialog.PrintDocument%2A>

trans-unit.source: In that sense, the control can be used as an unseen printing component.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen kan brukes på den måten som en unseen utskrift komponent.

trans-unit.source: But for performance reasons, it would be better to use either the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AddJob%2A> method or one of the many <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.Write%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WriteAsync%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter>.
trans-unit.target: Men hensyn til ytelsen, vil det være bedre å bruke enten <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AddJob%2A>metoden eller en av de mange <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.Write%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WriteAsync%2A>metoder for <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter>.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WriteAsync%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.Write%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AddJob%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more about this, see [How to: Programmatically Print XPS Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om dette, kan du se [slik: programmatisk utskrift XPS filer](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Do not confuse this class, PrintDialog, with <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Ikke forveksle denne klassen, PrintDialog, med <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The latter is used with Windows Forms applications.
trans-unit.target: Det siste brukes med Windows Forms-programmer.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that is used by the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialog"></xref> when the user clicks **Print** for the current print job.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som brukes av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialog"> </xref> når brukeren klikker **skrive ut** for gjeldende utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: Neither setting nor getting this property validates the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.
trans-unit.target: Verken angir eller henter egenskapen validerer <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: To validate it use <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Ikke valideres Bruk <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that is used the next time the **Print** button in the dialog box is clicked.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som brukes neste gang den **Skriv ut** -knappen i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Setting this PrintTicket property does not validate or modify the specified <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> for a particular <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angi egenskapen PrintTicket ikke validere eller endre den angitte <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> for en bestemt <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If needed, use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket*> method to create a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>-specific <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that is valid for a given printer.
trans-unit.target: Om nødvendig kan du bruke den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket*>metode for å opprette en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>-spesifikke <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som er gyldig for en gitt skriver.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket*>
